$$title: Kinetic Gas Theory
 
 <math>PV = nRT</math>  
 <math>R= 8.3 J/K</math>

1 mol = about 24 liters

 <math>PV = NkT</math>  
 <math>k = \frac{R}{avogadro}</math>

Assuming temperature is constant (isothermal atmosphere)
 <math> P_h = P_o e^{\frac{-h}{H_o}}</math> H_0 = 8km



